@startuml arch_b_sequence
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #336699
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #336699
skinparam sequenceBoxBackgroundColor #EEF3FF
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

title Architecture B — N-Tier Synchronous Flow\n(Synchronous Layered Architecture Pattern)

actor "Student\n(Browser)" as S
participant "Presentation Layer\n(FastAPI Router)" as P #LightBlue
participant "Business Logic Layer\n(AggregatorFacade)" as B #LightYellow
participant "RSSAdapter\n(Feedparser XML)" as RSS #LightGreen
participant "AdzunaAdapter\n(REST API)" as ADZ #LightGreen
participant "JoobleAdapter\n(REST API)" as JOO #LightGreen
participant "Data Access Layer\n(SQLAlchemy ORM)" as DAL #LightSalmon
database "PostgreSQL\n(Storage Layer)" as DB #Wheat

S  -> P   : GET /api/feeds/rss?category=internship
activate P
P  -> B   : fetch_all_opportunities()
activate B

note right of B : All external calls happen\nSYNCHRONOUSLY within the\nsame HTTP request lifecycle

B  -> RSS : fetch_opportunities()
activate RSS
RSS --> B : List[NormalizedRssItem]\n(~800–1000 ms)
deactivate RSS

B  -> ADZ : fetch_opportunities()
activate ADZ
ADZ --> B : List[NormalizedRssItem]\n(~200–500 ms)
deactivate ADZ

B  -> JOO : fetch_opportunities()
activate JOO
JOO --> B : List[NormalizedRssItem]\n(~300–600 ms)
deactivate JOO

B  -> B   : deduplicate(items)\n[in-memory set() pass]

B  -> DAL : insert_all(items)
activate DAL
DAL -> DB : INSERT INTO rss_items\nON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
activate DB
DB --> DAL: OK
deactivate DB
deactivate DAL

B  -> DAL : select(category, page, limit)
activate DAL
DAL -> DB : SELECT * FROM rss_items\nWHERE category = ?\nORDER BY published_at DESC\nLIMIT ? OFFSET ?
activate DB
DB --> DAL: rows
deactivate DB
DAL --> B : List[NormalizedRssItem]
deactivate DAL

B  --> P  : merged + filtered result
deactivate B

P  --> S  : HTTP 200 JSON\n(Total: ~1500–2600 ms)
deactivate P

note over S, DB : ⚠️  PROBLEM: If ANY external API hangs,\nthe student waits the full timeout duration.\nJooble timeout (15s) = blank page for student.

@enduml
